Plan and Test with Scale Test
Book a slot on your sandbox instance calendar and test at production peak load. Compare performance data from recent tests. Get in-app notifications and email confirmations about booking start times, end times, and cancellations.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in all editions.
Who: Scale Test is available for customers with a full copy sandbox in all Hyperforce regions except for Singapore.
How: To get access, contact your customer success representative or account executive. From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Scale, and then click Scale Test.
